id\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a thrilling 100m breaststroke final, China's Quinting Tang led the race for about 95m, with Ireland's Mona McSharry and Italy's Benedetto Pilato also in podium positions down the home stretch.\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9997275851130494, \"rank\": 0.00020032247215321964, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 542, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_dynasty\", \"score\": 0.9999873174219172, \"rank\": 1.0749505285834597e-05, \"text\": \"Tang\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_dynasty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_dynasty\"}, {\"begin\": 580, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9998762731516211, \"rank\": 0.0001237415906093558, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 590, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mona McSharry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\"}, {\"begin\": 608, \"end\": 613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9379876882031447, \"rank\": 0.06553904848252799, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benedetto_Croce\", \"score\": 0.9999999992064659, \"rank\": 6.289270017126186e-10, \"text\": \"Benedetto\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benedetto_Croce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benedetto_Croce\"}, {\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Pilato\", \"score\": 0.9999999318351934, \"rank\": 5.771622088724473e-08, \"text\": \"Pilato\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Pilato\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Pilato\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tatjana, who was in fourth place when they turned at the wall, but she fought her way back into contention in the final 50m of the swim, as she first moved past Pilato and McSharry before beating Tang as the first swimmer totouch the wall for gold.\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Pilato\", \"score\": 0.9999999318351934, \"rank\": 5.771622088724473e-08, \"text\": \"Pilato\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Pilato\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Pilato\"}, {\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_dynasty\", \"score\": 0.9999873174219172, \"rank\": 1.0749505285834597e-05, \"text\": \"Tang\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_dynasty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_dynasty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her super victory bringsSouth Africa's medal tally to three, after the Blitzboks won bronze in the rugby andmountain biker Alan Hatherlyalso secured bronze in the men's cross-country race.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Blitzboks\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This means Team SA has already equalled its medal tally of the 2020 Olympics, when they had scooped a gold and two silver medals.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1138, \"end\": 1140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.814012715364254e-19, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"\\\"I did not want to focus on anyone,\\\" Tatjana said after her golden swim.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew the only way I could be the best version of myself was to focus on my own race.\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1414, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just so grateful it was my hands that touched first.\\\"\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the final, if you have a lane, you have a chance.\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we were all fighting,\\\" an emotional Tatjana  added.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The emotions were really \\u2026 it took a village to get me where I am today.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know they would have been proud, even if I did not get a medal, but it was really for them,\\\" Smith said.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was for everyone that has been with me, who believed in me and for my country as well.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our hashtag is 'for my country \\u2026' it really is, just to inspire someone at home and to know that they do not have to disqualify themselves and potentially be an Olympic champion,\\\" Tatjana further explained.\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the work is not done, I still have the 200 to go!\\\"\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2128, \"end\": 2131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999998391968021, \"rank\": 1.1069378973365722e-07, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 2132, \"end\": 2134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.9605642941117408, \"rank\": 0.04083754479726986, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on Facebook for the latest local and international news  Follow The South African's WhatsApp channel for the latest sport, lifestyle and local news  Follow The South African on X for the latest, breaking news  A brand new shopping mall is coming to Pretoria East, bringing major retailers and new convenience to the area.\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2356, \"end\": 2364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9999997162931724, \"rank\": 2.837070147232939e-07, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": 